In [213]:
# We have to prepare a prediction model for profit.
# Our dependent variable(or attribute) is Profit.
# From above table we can see there is strong correlation between "profit and R&D Spend" as well as "profit and Marketing Spend".
# Marketing Spend and R&D Spend are also correlated.
# From the assumptions of Multiple regression model, we know that there should not be multicolinearity in the data.So we will
# build two models considering R&D Spend and Marketing Spend one at a time and then decide the better model.
